divs: Sighting Detailswhile visiting Tucson over Thanksgiving and staying at the Hilton El Conquistador hotel, I stepped out of my hotel room to admire the full moon over the mountains. I took a picture of the moon and mountains. When I looked at the pic on my computer, I saw an object in the sky. Note that I did not see the object with my eye but only in the picture. This was not dust on my camera as I have another pic that was taken a minute later that has no blemish. Believe what you will. the Pic is attached.
